                     <p>
                        <placeName key="place_108025">Staverton</placeName>.

   <persName>
                           <persName>J<supplied>ohn</supplied>
                           </persName> 
                           <surname>P<supplied>hilip</supplied>
                           </surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_108031">W<supplied>eltone</supplied>
                           </placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName>
                           <forename>Alice</forename> de  <surname>Bradewelle</surname>
                        </persName>, daughter of the late <persName>
                           <forename>Hugh</forename> de  <surname>Bradewelle</surname>
                        </persName>, his wife, grant to <orgName key="org_108004">D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                        </orgName> a house in <placeName key="place_108025">Stavertone</placeName>, with part of a court, lying between the tenement of <persName>
                           <forename>Adam</forename> 
                           <surname>Kynge</surname>
                        </persName> and that late of <persName>
                           <forename>Hugh</forename> de <surname>Bradewelle</surname>
                        </persName>, with 2 acres of arable land in S<supplied>taverton</supplied> viz.
<pb n="112"/>
½ acre in the South field over <placeName type="minor">Overcaldewellehul</placeName> by <persName>
                           <forename>Roger</forename> 
                           <surname>Evermond</surname>
                        </persName>’s land and ½ acre in <placeName type="minor">Combesmede</placeName>; ½ acre in the north field under <placeName type="minor">le Schonele</placeName> by <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> 
                           <surname>Abbey</surname>
                        </persName>’s land; one rood in <placeName type="minor">Holecombe mede</placeName>, one rood in <placeName type="minor">Foxhole mede</placeName>. Given at <placeName role="date" key="place_108012">D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                        </placeName>. 
   Witnesses: <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> 
                           <surname>Frennche</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_108025">Stavertone</placeName>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> le <surname>Frennche</surname>
                        </persName> of the same, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>Nicholas</forename> 
                           <surname>Ro</surname>
                        </persName> of the same, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>Robert</forename> le <surname>West</surname>, senior</persName> of the same, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>Richard</forename> de <surname>aula</surname>
                        </persName> of the same,
   <persName>
                           <forename>Simon</forename> 
                           <surname>Bawdewyne</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_108012">D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                           </placeName>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>Geoffrey</forename> de <surname>aula</surname>
                        </persName> of the same, 
   <persName>
